在[[信息技术|信息技术]]（IT）和[[系统管理|系统管理]]领域，'''IT运营分析'''（IT operations analytics，'''ITOA'''）是一种检索、分析和报告IT运营数据的方法或手段。<ref name="DataJournal">{{cite web|title=The Time Has Come: Analytics Delivers for IT Operations|url=http://www.datacenterjournal.com/it/time-analytics-delivers-operations/|publisher=Data Center Journal|accessdate=2013-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130224072609/http://www.datacenterjournal.com/it/time-analytics-delivers-operations/|archive-date=2013-02-24|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref name="Fletcher">{{citation|last=Fletcher|first=Colin|title=Apply IT Operations Analytics to Broader Datasets for Greater Business Insight|url=http://www.gartner.com/document/2778217|date=2014-06-24|access-date=2015-09-29}}</ref>{{link-en|Forrester Research}}将IT运营分析定义为 "利用数学算法和其他创新，从管理和监控技术收集的海量原始数据中提取有意义的信息<ref>{{cite web|title=Turn Big Data Inward With IT Analytics|url=https://www.forrester.com/Turn+Big+Data+Inward+With+IT+Analytics/fulltext/-/E-RES75501?objectid=RES75501|publisher=Forrester Research|accessdate=2012-12-05|archive-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113145009/https://www.forrester.com/Turn+Big+Data+Inward+With+IT+Analytics/fulltext/-/E-RES75501?objectid=RES75501}}</ref>。"而運用到[[人工智能|人工智能]]和[[机器学习|机器学习]]的ITOA又被稱為'''AIOps'''（Artificial Intelligence for IT Operations）。AIOps這一概念由[[高德纳|高德纳]]於2016年提出<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://diginomica.com/moogsoft-ceo-phil-tee-aiops-and-service-assurance-age-digital-transformation|title=AIOps and service assurance in the age of digital transformation|publisher=Diginomica|author=Jerry Bowles|date=2020-01-28|access-date=2021-03-15|archive-date=2021-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424131444/https://diginomica.com/moogsoft-ceo-phil-tee-aiops-and-service-assurance-age-digital-transformation}}</ref>。

